Sentencas: K2NiF4 structured La2Co0.8Ni0.2O4+delta is an oxygen overstoichiometric oxide with high oxygen diffusion and oxygen surface exchange coefficients at temperature range 450-800 degrees C.
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, composites consisting of La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+delta (LSCN, x=O, 0.4, 0.8, 1.2, 1.6) and Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (GDC) have been investigated as the cathodes for low-and-intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: AC impedance spectroscopy on symmetric cells indicated that among the series of LSCN-GDC composites, La1.2Sr0.8Co0.8Ni0.2O4+delta-based electrode had the lowest interfacial polarization resistance, which was 1.36 Omega cm(2) at 600 degrees C when the electrode was not activated.
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Significant activation effect was observed with a single cell when current treatment was performed at 200 mA cm(-2) within 30 min.
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The single cell with La1.2Sr0.8Co0.8Ni0.2O4+delta-GDC as the cathode generated power density up to 350mW cm(-2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, the performance was pretty stable when a constant output voltage of 0.5 V was set for 36 h. These results suggest that La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+delta could be promising materials as the cathodes for SOFCs that operated at low-and-intennediate temperatures.
Titulo: K2NiF4 type La2-xSrxCo0.8Ni0.2O4+δ as the cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells
